description: Locally owned and proud to be serving the Mile High City the finest desserts, The Dessert Stand has just the treat for you! From gourmet cupcakes such as Chocolate Salted Caramel, Tropical Paradise, Key Lime Pie, Cookie Dough and Birthday Cake to our mini pies, krispy treat pops, cupcake push pops, cookies, vintage soda and more, we are sure to leave your sweet tooth satisfied!
name: The Dessert Stand
